<script type="text/javascript">
function OnVisilabsCartLoaded() {
    var pbid = {{RMC-ecommerce.cart.basket_id}};
    var pbArray = {{RMC-CartArray-PB-JS}};
    var puArray = {{RMC-CartArray-PU-JS}};
    var pprArray = {{RMC-CartArray-PPR-JS}};
    var pbt = {{RMC-CartArray-PBT-JS}};
    var pb = pbArray.join(';');
    var pu = puArray.join(';');
    var ppr = pprArray.join(';');
    var exceptionArray = ['null', 'undefined', ''];
    var exception = false;
    var VL = new Visilabs();
    for (var index = 0; index < pbArray.length; index++) {
        var productCode = pbArray[index];
        var productQty = puArray[index];
        var productPrice = pprArray[index];
        if (!pbid || !productCode || !productQty || !productPrice || exceptionArray.includes(productCode) || isNaN(productQty) || isNaN(productPrice)) {
            exception = true;
            break;
        }
    }
    if (exception) {
        VL.AddParameter("OM.VLEventException", "True");
        VL.AddParameter("OM.VLEventExceptionName", "ProductBasket");
        VL.Collect();
    } else {
        VL.AddParameter("OM.pbid", pbid);
        VL.AddParameter("OM.pb", pb);
        VL.AddParameter("OM.pu", pu)
        VL.AddParameter("OM.ppr", ppr);
        VL.AddParameter("OM.pbt", pbt);
        VL.Collect();
        VL.SuggestActions();
    }
}


if(typeof Visilabs !== 'function'){
    var url = (location.protocol.indexOf("https")==0?"https":"http") + "://vsh.visilabs.net/Visilabs.min.js?sid="+{{RMC-sid}}+"&oid="+{{RMC-oid}}+"";
    var script = document.createElement("script");
    if(location.href.toString().indexOf("vldebug=true") > 0){url = (location.protocol.indexOf("https")==0?"https":"http") + "://vsh.visilabs.net/Visilabs_Debug.js?sid="+{{RMC-sid}}+"&oid="+{{RMC-oid}}+"";}
    script.onload = OnVisilabsCartLoaded;
    script.type = "text/javascript";
    script.src = url;
    document.getElementsByTagName("head")[0].appendChild(script);
}else OnVisilabsCartLoaded();
</script>

<script type="text/javascript">
function OnVisilabsProductLoaded() {
    var product = {{RMC-ecommerce.detail.product}}
    var vl = new Visilabs();
    
    var exceptionArray = ['null', 'undefined', ''];
    if(product && product.id && product.name && product.price && !exceptionArray.includes(product.id) && !exceptionArray.includes(product.name) && !isNaN(product.price)){
        vl.AddParameter("OM.pv", product.id);
        vl.AddParameter("OM.pn", product.name);
        vl.AddParameter("OM.ppr", product.price);
        if(product.stock && !isNaN(product.stock)){
            vl.AddParameter("OM.inv", product.stock);
        }
        if(product.brand && !exceptionArray.includes(product.brand)){
            vl.AddParameter("OM.pv.1", product.brand);
        }
        if(product.category && !exceptionArray.includes(product.category)){
            vl.AddParameter("OM.cat", product.category);
        }
    }else {
        vl.AddParameter("OM.VLEventException", "True");
        vl.AddParameter("OM.VLEventExceptionName", "ProductView");
      var url=window.location.href;
      vl.AddParameter("OM.pageUrl", url);
    }
    vl.Collect();
    vl.SuggestActions();
}

<script>
function HealthTrigger(){
    var VL = new Visilabs();
    var loginRule =document.querySelector(".user-name"); // Sayfa da giriş yapıp yada kayıt olduktan sonra gelen merhaba yada user isimini içeren HTML elemanı
    var url=document.location.href; // Sayfa URL i 
    var path=document.location.pathname; // Sayfa Path i
    var elemProduct= document.querySelector(".product-page"); // Product sayfasını belirleyen Eleman yada URL bilgisi
    var elemCategory= document.querySelector(".list__body"); // Category sayfasını belirleyen Eleman yada URL bilgisi
    
    
    if(loginRule && VisiParameters["OM.exvisitorID"] ){
        VL.AddParameter("OM.VLControlEventException", "True");
        VL.AddParameter("OM.VLControlEventExceptionName", "Login or Sign Up");
        console.log("Login Signup eventinde hata var");
    }
    
    if(elemProduct && !VisiParameters["OM.pv"]){
        VL.AddParameter("OM.VLControlEventException", "True");
        VL.AddParameter("OM.VLControlEventExceptionName", "Product View");
        console.log("Product view eventinde hata var");
    }
    
    if(elemCategory && !VisiParameters["OM.clist"]){
        VL.AddParameter("OM.VLControlEventException", "True");
        VL.AddParameter("OM.VLControlEventExceptionName", "Category Page View");
        console.log("Category view eventinde hata var");
    }
    
    
    if(url.includes("/baskets/basket/") &&!VisiParameters["OM.pbid"]){
        VL.AddParameter("OM.VLControlEventException", "True");
        VL.AddParameter("OM.VLControlEventExceptionName", "Product Basket");
        console.log("CartView eventinde hata var");
    }
    
    
    if(url.includes("/orders/completed/") &&!VisiParameters["OM.tid"]){
        VL.AddParameter("OM.VLControlEventException", "True");
        VL.AddParameter("OM.VLControlEventExceptionName", "Product Purchase");
        console.log("Purchase eventinde hata var");
    }
    
    if(url.includes("search_text") && !VisiParameters["OM.OSS"] ){
        VL.AddParameter("OM.VLControlEventException", "True");
        VL.AddParameter("OM.VLControlEventExceptionName", "On Site Search");
        console.log("Search eventinde hata var");
    }
    
VL.Collect();
VL.SuggestActions();
}
